task.summary: Added the functionality of having the license in the config. Improved security
The plugin now makes a void world called FFA.
Added a /kp map command to teleport to the map
Added the kitpvp realname command to find the real name of a nicked player.
Fixed max 32 characters in Bounty Hunter {PlayerName} bug
You can now see a suffix before buying it.
Fixed the Kit shop and Cosmetic Shop
Updated the version in the plugin.yml
Fixed the Bounty Hunter GUI and updated the freeze gui
